This helps you get started with GCP

Get a Google Cloud Platform account
https://cloud.google.com/gcp/

Install the GCP SDK
https://cloud.google.com/sdk/docs/quickstart-debian-ubuntu
make sure you copy the entire command line from this quickstart - it's easy to copy part of the line and it will create a problem

Start to learn and use gsutil
gsutil cp ./index.html gs://www.yourbucket
gsutil acl ch -u AllUsers:R gs://www.yourbucket.com/index.html
